entries.s_49709fbf: We're clenching our fists tighter around the Rebel Alliance. Soon, they won't be in existence. They're nothing but trouble. You should stay away from them.
entries.s_3626560c: Visalis is on our side. If he wins the election, more Imperial Troops will be recruited and sent to Bestine. I hear the Tusken Raiders are getting restless. You should vote. The governor is taking them over at the capitol. Oh-break is over. Move along, citizen.
